(10, 'Coloring Master ASMR', 'Casual', 'Bounce Entertainment Company Limited', '1,000,000+', 'Create your own masterpiece or get inspiration and browse through thousands of beautiful coloring pages in our gallery created by our awesome Coloring Pages Master!\nComplete hundreds of beautiful pictures, improve your art skills and soothe your mind with this bright, creative and relaxing game for players of all ages.\n\nGame features\n? Hundred styles of different themes for painting include animals ? , birds ? , fruit ? and nature ?, and so much more.\n? Line and color: first draw the following line of the object, then color the space to complete the picture. And remember to pick colors to match the order, the more matches the color, the higher accuracy you will get! However, if you want to think out of the box and go freestyle, it’s up to you! \n? Improve your art skill: all pictures in Coloring Pages Master are well-designed and you can use them as templates to recreate your own art and improve your drawing, painting skills in the process. \n? Relieve your stress and unleash your creativity: take your time in Coloring Pages Master to soothe your nerves and relieve your stress away with therapeutic drawing and coloring method. \n\nRelax and enjoy all the fun of coloring and drawing without any mess or expensive materials, right on your device, Coloring Pages Master is your first choice. Download this delightful virtual coloring book on your device right now and have a good time relaxing and creating your artwork.\n\n\nWe update the game regularly with your suggestions, so leave us a review and we’ll do our best to improve the game.\n \nFollow Us:\n* Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/bouncegamestudio\n* Website: https://www.bounce.com.vn\n* Email: contact@bounce.com.vn', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=bounce.Coloring.Pages', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/QF4fNkK1H8s-szrz0wVK3Zy9QVFeBSJ-SKlDQRMM-rU48G0FXAo-iXjVJa0YiqNmREsv'),
