(12, 'Shotgun Sounds: Gun Simulator', 'Simulation', 'DINO Global LTD', '1,000,000+', 'Hold, charge, press the gun trigger, and enjoy real life gunshot sounds in Shotgun Sounds: Gun Simulator. \n\nShotgun Sounds: Gun Simulator is a safe gun-app simulator that helps you experience the feeling of using gun without any threat to anyone. Explore a wide collection of realistic and fake guns, listen to gun shooting sounds as well as other powerful weapons sounds to serve your passion for warfare and powerful weapons. You\'ll adapt to different shooting environments and become a gunshot sound enthusiast. \n\nEnjoy the real life gunshot sounds and motions of your guns. Pick up your favorite gun and shoot your target now!\n\nHOW TO PLAY: \n? Scroll to choose the weapons on the home screen\n? Tap to get gunfire or explosion sounds.\n? Swipe to recharge \n? Free to adjust: \n- Select Gun Simulator Mode: Single Shot, Burst Mode, Auto Shot, and Shake\n- Select Diversity Environment: Rain, Snow, Thunder\n\nFEATURES: \n? Extremely smooth, responsive, and easy to use the sound of the gun app\n? Various powerful weapons collection from different categories: Pistol, machine, rifle, revolver, shotgun,...\n? Exciting gunshot gameplay sound of gun\n? Wonderful UI/UX of the sound of gun\n? High-quality shot animations like vibration during play sound of gun.\n? Thrilling Effects and Gun Sounds.\n? Best AI used for developing to make the more amazing sound of gun.\n? Increase your gun knowledge or use the sound of gun to prank your friends\n\nAre you ready to become a gun master? Enjoy the realistic gunshot sounds. Download Shotgun Sounds: Gun Simulator and find out now!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gun.simulator.sounds', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/kciS8kXK_K24IXWHBK2TPGqhQToRDR_zm8U6cEJskUnv382WQBst2MmKsJBD9UzcHcUa'),
(13, 'Candy Crush Saga', 'Casual', 'King', '1,000,000,000+', 'Master the legendary match 3 puzzle game from King! With over a trillion matching levels played, Candy Crush Saga is one of the most popular match 3 puzzle games of all time.\n\nMatch, pop, and blast candies in this tasty puzzle adventure to progress to the next level and get a sugar blast! Master match 3 puzzles with quick thinking and smart matching moves to be rewarded with sugar bonuses and tasty candy combos.\n\nPlan your moves by matching 3 or more candies in a row and blast your way through the extra sticky puzzles using lollipop hammers! Blast jam and chocolate to collect sweet candy juice across thousands of puzzle levels, guaranteed to have you craving more!\n\nBECOME THE MASTER OF THE CANDY KINDGOM\nWin thousands of matching puzzles: with new puzzles added every 2 weeks, your sugar fix is never far away!\n\nWIN CANDYLICIOUS REWARDS\nSpin the Daily Booster Wheel to receive lollipop hammers and other tasty rewards! Master time-limited match 3 challenges to earn boosters and clear the jelly! \n\nVARIETY OF SUGAR-COATED PUZZLE CHALLENGES\nSweet ways to play! Play match 3 game modes and more including Target Score, Clear the Jelly, and Collect the Ingredients. \n\nLevel up playing match 3 puzzles that range from easy to hard, accessible online or offline.\n\nBLAST CANDIES WITH FRIENDS\nMatch and pop candies to get to the top of the leaderboard! Compare scores with friends and find out who’s the match 3 master!\n\nEnjoy the sweetest match 3 puzzle game around! \n\nIf you want to master and blast even more puzzles, you may also enjoy Candy Crush Soda Saga, Farm Heroes Saga, and Pet Rescue Saga.\n\nCandy Crush Saga is free to play but optional in-game items require payment. You can turn off the payment feature by disabling in-app purchases in your device’s settings.\n\nBy downloading Candy Crush Saga you agree to our terms of service which can be found at https://king.com/termsAndConditions\n\nDo not s